---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Meet the team behind Madrid Amor — Arturo, a Madrid photographer who studied at Korea University and lived in Seoul, and [ENSO], your Korean coordinator. Together we capture love stories in Madrid."
  currentPage="about"
  alternateKo="/ko/about/"
>
  <!-- Hero Image -->
  <section class="py-2">
    <img
      src="/images/arturo-photographer.jpg"
      alt="Arturo - Madrid Amor Photographer"
      class="w-full h-[70vh] object-cover"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- About Text -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="content-narrow text-block-centered">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-4">Your Team</p>
      <h1>Meet Arturo & [ENSO]</h1>

      <p class="mt-8">
        Hello! I'm Arturo, the photographer behind Madrid Amor. But my story isn't just about
        Madrid — it's also about Korea. I lived in Seoul for two years, studied at Korea University
        (고려대학교), and worked at the Spanish Embassy in Korea. Those years gave me a deep love
        for Korean culture, and when I came back to Madrid, I knew I wanted to create something
        special for Korean couples visiting my city.
      </p>

      <p>
        That's why I work together with [ENSO], [ENSO_ROL_DESCRIPCION]. [ENSO_BACKGROUND].
        When you reach out to Madrid Amor, [ENSO] is the person you'll be talking to — she makes
        sure everything feels easy and comfortable from your very first message.
      </p>

      <p>
        Together, we bridge two worlds. I bring the photography, the knowledge of Madrid's most
        beautiful spots, and the golden Spanish light. [ENSO] brings [ENSO_CUALIDADES].
        We're not just a photography service — we're your friends in Madrid.
      </p>

      <p>
        When we're not preparing for photoshoots, you'll find us exploring Madrid's hidden gems —
        from secret rooftop terraces to quiet plazas that most tourists never discover. These are
        the places we love to share with the couples we photograph.
      </p>

      <!-- Instagram -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
        <a
          href="https://instagram.com/arturo_madrid_weddings"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-600 hover:text-terracotta transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
