          @arturo_madrid_weddings
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Madrid Section -->
  <section class="py-2">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
      <img src="/images/gallery/photo-7.jpg" alt="Madrid street photography" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover" />
      <img src="/images/gallery/photo-8.jpg" alt="Madrid golden hour" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover" />
      <img src="/images/gallery/photo-9.jpg" alt="Madrid romantic location" class="w-full aspect-square object-cover" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="content-narrow text-block-centered">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-4">The Location</p>
      <h2>Why Madrid?</h2>

      <p class="mt-8">
        Madrid isn't just Spain's capital — it's a city that breathes romance. With over 300 days
        of sunshine per year, the famous Spanish light creates a warm, golden glow that photographers
        dream of.
      </p>

      <p>
        From the grandeur of the Royal Palace to the charming streets of Malasaña, from the tranquil
        gardens of Retiro Park to the dramatic sunset views at Temple of Debod — Madrid offers an
        incredible diversity of backdrops for your love story. And because Arturo knows every corner
        of this city — and [ENSO] knows exactly what Korean couples love — we'll plan a route that
        feels both authentically Madrid and perfectly you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial -->
  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="content-narrow text-block-centered">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-8">Kind Words</p>
      <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8" style="font-family: 'Chulapa', Georgia, serif;">
        "From the first WhatsApp message to the final gallery, everything was so easy. Arturo knew
        exactly where to take us and [ENSO] helped us plan every detail. It felt like having friends
        in Madrid."
      </blockquote>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
        Sarah & Michael, Honeymoon 2024
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="content-narrow text-block-centered">
      <h2>Let's Create Something Beautiful</h2>
      <p class="my-6">
        We'd love to hear about your plans. Send us a message and let's start planning your Madrid love story together.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-simple">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
